data.description: Introducing this charming single-level home, boasting four spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms, making it the perfect family haven. As you approach, the front landscaping welcomes you with its lush greenery and fabulous curb appeal, setting a picturesque scene. Step inside, and you’ll be greeted by the open floor plan with new flooring and double sided fireplace that exude a sense of elegance and style. The heart of this home is its newly renovated kitchen, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, sleek new cabinets, and a large pantry for all your storage needs. The kitchen also boasts a convenient island, perfect for meal preparation and casual dining.Throughout the house, you’ll notice updated elements that enhance both functionality and aesthetics. The plantation shutters add a touch of sophistication while allowing natural light to fill the rooms. The house is not only stylish but also energy-efficient, thanks to the addition of solar panels, ensuring sustainable living for the environmentally conscious. The garage features the option for three parking spaces with a pull through door to the backyard and RV parking for your convenience. Newly installed wooden fence and awnings will provide comfort while enjoying your backyard. With its thoughtful design, modern amenities, and attention to detail, this house offers a comfortable and luxurious living experience for you and your family. Welcome home to a space where every detail has been carefully crafted to create a harmonious blend of functionality and beauty.
